dc_title_s: Map of the Perth Amboy Shore of Staten Island Sound from Fayette Street to Buckingham Avenue Locating the existing Pierhead and Bulkhead Lines with reference to High Street
dc_description_s: Map labels the various companies located along the waters edge including Raritan Dry Dock Co., Perth Amboy Dry Dock Co., Standard Oil Co., Merritt's Wharf, and Raritan Mercantile Co.|Map was traced from blueprint Sep. 27, 1917 by H.R. Tooker.
